title: Dembélé, the unloved one forgiven!
body:
Dembélé, the unloved one forgiven!

Atlético de Madrid nearly managed the perfect holdup in front of Barça this Saturday in the clash at the top of the 13th day of La Liga. But Ousmane Dembélé, entered 10 minutes earlier, equalized at the last minute (1-1).

The diabolical plan of Diego Simeone was close to working. A low block, concrete, no risk taking but set kicks exploited thoroughly. This is how Atlético de Madrid thought…
